channel.description:
Okay I'm just sitting here laughing my ass off while xiionz is sending me these screenie of this kid (zest haha)
First it started off as him asking zest why he's pissed at me then it turned into all this:
[u][b]Repo = Zest Jonathan = Xiionz[/b][/u] [img]http://img233.imageshack.us/img233/7348/f0a5dbc3bb4645e4875909f.png[/img] [img]http://img23.imageshack.us/img23/4063/98105d74853a427985af3e4.png[/img] [img]http://img683.imageshack.us/img683/254/a5363876e38240fe8fd303b.png[/img]
don't you agree this kid repo is a lil high strong about coding and doesn't spend enough time for school, this kid has a D in math just to add and this guy is 14.
